## Resume Summary

**Hybrid Physics–ML Wind Farm Layout Optimization**  
Python · NumPy · SciPy · XGBoost · Matplotlib · Jupyter

- Designed a constrained non-convex optimization framework to maximize wind farm AEP using Jensen wake modeling, turbine power curves, and spacing/boundary constraints over a 20 km² spatial wind resource grid.
- Implemented and benchmarked multiple solvers (penalty gradient descent, L-BFGS-B, SLSQP, multistart), analyzing convergence behavior, feasibility, and runtime scaling.
- Built an XGBoost surrogate trained on 10k+ physics-labeled turbine layouts to accelerate layout evaluation by ~90%, with top candidates refined and validated using the full simulator.
- Delivered a reproducible ML + optimization pipeline with benchmark reports, convergence visualizations, and sensitivity analysis for wind direction and spacing parameters.

